----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Gather Merge
   Workers Planned: 2
   ->  Sort
         Sort Key: pctest_h1.k, pctest_h2.k
         ->  Hash Join
               Hash Cond: ((pctest_h2.a = pctest_h1.a) AND (pctest_h2.c = pctest_h1.c))
               ->  Parallel Seq Scan on pctest_h2
               ->  Hash
                     ->  Seq Scan on pctest_h1
